‐ No need to shower at work (due to minimal exertion) 	‐ Less exercise or recreational value when compared to pedal cycling
‐ Less overall effort (compared to regular bikes) 	‐ Awkward and heavy to carry battery in public
‐ Commute time more enjoyable 	
